{"tid":290282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]巴黎香榭麗舍大道一汽車衝向警車起火","createTime":"2017-06-19T15:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T01:13:26.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4824f3d557b207288699d5637e63575f7ae2f8a","tid":290282,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕法國巴黎香榭麗舍大街今天發生一輛汽車衝撞警車並起火的事件，所幸並沒有造成任何傷亡。現在警方已經封鎖現場，有一名男子被捕，不過目前還不清楚是否為攻擊事件。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，法國巴黎香榭麗舍大街19日發生汽車衝撞警車事件，汽車隨即起火燃燒。警方隨後封鎖現場，並呼籲民眾避開封鎖區，警方表示這起事件並沒有造成任何傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n法國媒體報導指出有一名男子被捕，但目前仍不清楚這是單純事故還是攻擊事件，現在現場有非常多持槍的武警與警車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2105491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2105491&d=jUXM8SRHKERaV9JIver5ZE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=84d92fa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2105491&h=5a05f2f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2105491</a>"},{"pid":"0bd2b3434ff22c1b3763deee943b12fb0d7004d2","tid":290282,"uid":89343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3874f06230ecd7f76c49d551c319bdd452050b","tid":290282,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭國？"},{"pid":"8c5fc9c05c3929a7f635d62c7b2a470eb7c185e7","tid":290282,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"雙城記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e5f8257de440449e5c89b664b605656086c129","tid":290282,"uid":60206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"其實點解係狂攻法國?"},{"pid":"1e86cb8f84d731498ba6e55f509c22a07a76c4a7","tid":29028